 example in colorectal cancer which led to\nobtaining the parameters describing the surrogate relationships with higher\nprecision.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 May 2019 10:58:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2019 11:22:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-05"}
